headline.main: Rescue Helicopter Crashes in Central Japan; At Least 3 Dead
headline.print_headline: Rescue Helicopter Crashes in Central Japan; At Least 3 Dead

lead_paragraph: The leader of the populist, euroskeptic Finns Party says that he will step down in June when the party votes for a new chairman, leaving no clear leader to take over.
